title: Earthlings WeWow Day 5
description:
Mindy and Guy Raz are on the road listening to your messages for Day 5 of Earthlings WeWow! Then, we're all listening to the new Tinkercast Original Podcast, Flip and Mozi's Guide to How to be an Earthling! After the show, don't forget to search for Flip and Mozi wherever you get your podcasts so you can subscribe to download new episodes as they air on Thursdays!
